parameters:
Anomalocaris: Hey, are you working seriously? Just because
the organization got absorbed, don't you start slacking off
on our turf!

Memimi: Hmph... Who would do such a cowardly thing... You
should be the one to behave in a manner worthy of my
service... Your taste in costumes is also terrible...

Anomalocaris: All you do is talk back! Maybe it's because
Bunny-chan didn't discipline you properly, huh?!

Memimi: Don't hit them!!! I won't forgive you, you bastard,
grrrrr...!

Lackey: Boss, I've collected the protection money! We've
increased the protection fee by 1.3 times for all the shops
in Shark Broccoli's territory. These guys are idiots,
protecting their shops for such a cheap fee... Are they
stupid or what?

Anomalocaris: Moss! I can buy a new bike with this... From
next time, collect 1.5 times the amount! And for this
convenience store, raise the price of each plastic bag to 5
yen!

Memimi: (Doroku City is such that the mayor fattens his own
wallet with tax money, so there's virtually no support from
the city to its citizens... Running a shop in such a town is
incredibly tough...!)

Memimi: (That's exactly why our organization protects the
shops from trouble with a low protection fee! Most of the
money collected is poured into the infrastructure and
cleaning of our territory... And now, to increase it by 1.5
times...? For their own greed!)

Memimi: I can't stand it anymore!! Anomalocaris, I challenge
you to a Monster Fight!! Let's bet the organization once
more!!

Anomalocaris: Oh my... Are you sure about this? Challenging
me to a rematch, huh! Do you really have the resolve for
this?

Lackey: Gahaha! Don't you know the rules of Monster Fight?!
Rematches aren't something you can just do casually, man!

Monster Fight does not prohibit losers from seeking revenge
and trying to win back what they bet. However, to prevent
battles from becoming quagmires, there are strict conditions
for requesting a rematch.

Memimi: I know the rules! When challenging the same opponent
to a rematch, as a condition, the loser must obey any one
command from the winner, no matter what it is...

In Monster Fight, to achieve revenge, the loser must carry
out any one order issued by the winner. Naturally, to
prevent the winner from being robbed of what they won, these
orders are often extremely humiliating or dangerous. Since
this rule was established, there has never been a precedent
for an actual revenge match.

Memimi: Don't underestimate me... To take back the
organization and protect the public order of the city, I'll
wallow in as much mud as necessary. Think up whatever harsh
conditions you want!

Lackey: Whew! She's a crazy woman, willing to do whatever we
say! Boss, let's come up with something really tough!!
Anomalocaris: Yeah, hehehe... Hmm, what should it be?

Shark Broccoli: Orca Asparagus, I'm telling you it's a bad
idea... They're not going to give you any reasonable orders!
Don't be stubborn...

Memimi: Great Leader-sama, don't worry about me! I too am a
monster in my own right. There's nothing more painful than
remaining defeated!!

Memimi isn't stupid. Naturally, the conditions they will
come up with will be unimaginable. She might be lynched or
her body defiled. But even so, it's better to fight than to
continue being used by a corrupt organization.

Memimi: (...But please let it be something light...! I beg
you, make it something sensible with little damage...! And
especially avoid anything lewd or painful as much as
possible...!)

Anomalocaris: Alright, I've decided! The order I'm giving
you is... "Do a naked masturbation lap around the city"!!

Memimi: What?! "Do a naked masturbation lap around the
city"!!?
Memimi: Sorry, I didn't hear that clearly.

Lackey: You repeated it yourself! It's "do a naked
masturbation lap around the city", yeah, "do a naked
masturbation lap around the city"!!

Lackey: Of course, you gotta use the big streets with lots
of people passing by! And you can't hide your face or
identity, do it as Orca Asparagus himself!!

Memimi: (Around the city... naked?! And masturbation... that
kind of masturbation?! Naked...? Eeeehhh, naked masturbation
lap around the city...?)
Memimi: Let me think about it a bit.

Memimi: Ha... It's so ridiculously easy that I'm at a loss
for words... A naked masturbation is nothing for me. It's
not like I'll lose anything... Go ahead and advertise it
widely, gather a big crowd!

Anomalocaris: Oh, she's got spirit... Damn it, should I have
set something even tougher...?

Lackey: Isn't she embarrassed at all...? To be a high-
ranking official in a large organization, you gotta have
that kind of tough mentality, huh... gulp...

Underling: Orca Asparagus-sama, are you really going to
accept such conditions...? To go that far for the
organization... You're an amazing person...!

Memimi: (I've said it now... there's no turning back...
ughhhh... I'm really going to do a lap around the city...!)
//全体マップの試合会場での行先を試合2に変更

Memimi: Huh... It's not that big of a deal for me but...
right now is a bit... uh, the weather... Yeah, today was
supposed to be a day with strong UV rays... Yeah, too bad!

Memimi: (Ugh... What kind of condition is that... It's the
worst!! Do I have to resolve myself to do it...? No way...
doing masturbation in public...)
Memimi decided to back down for now...
